    "Conversely, Atleus outperforms GPU, 3D-TPU, and HAIMA, achieving consistent speedup through an efficient pipelined design that ensures high throughput.",
    "Further, ReRAM cores perform MVM operations in an energy-efficient manner without the need to fetch data from off-chip.",
    "F. Quantization EvaluationFinally, we evaluate the effectiveness of crossbar-wise quantization on Atleus.",
